additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Avoid contact with eyes and skin. May cause an allergic reaction in some individuals. For advice, contact a Poisons Information Centre (Phone Australia 13 11 26; New Zealand 0800 764 766) or a doctor. In case of contact with eyes or skin, rinse immediately with plenty of water. If irritation persists, seek medical advice. If swallowed, seek medical advice immediately and show this container or label. Keep out of reach of children and pets.
